  "prompt": "Who is the best mobile in 2016?",
  "response": "In 2016, several smartphones were highly regarded for their features, performance, and design. Some of the standout devices included:\n\n1. **Apple iPhone 7 and 7 Plus**: Known for their excellent cameras, performance, and ecosystem integration.\n2. **Samsung Galaxy S7 and S7 Edge**: Praised for their stunning displays, camera quality, and water resistance.\n3. **Google Pixel and Pixel XL**: Lauded for their stock Android experience and remarkable camera capabilities, particularly in low light.\n4. **OnePlus 3**: Appreciated for its value for money, offering high-end specs at a more affordable price.\n5. **LG G5**: Introduced a modular design, allowing users to swap out components for enhanced functionality.\n\nUltimately, the \"best\" mobile phone can be subjective and depends on individual preferences regarding operating systems, camera quality, design, and specific features.",
